<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <style>
        .a-upload{
            padding: 0px 10px;
            height: 28px;
            line-height: 28px;
            position: relative;
            z-index:0;
            border:1px solid #1164DF;
            color:#1164DF;
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: inline-block;
            float: left;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .a-upload span{

        }
        .a-upload input{
            position: absolute;
            z-index:9999;
            right: 0;
            top: 0;
            opacity: 0;
            filter: alpha(opacity=0);
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            height:30px;
        }
        .a-upload:hover{
            color: #FFFFFF;
            background: #1164DF;
            border-color: #1164DF;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .tip-error{
            clear: both;
            background: #F7F7FB;
            height:26px;
            line-height: 26px;
            width:100%;
        }
        .bt-error-close {display:inline-block;width:16px;height:16px;background: url(../images/cancel.png) no-repeat;float: right;margin: 5px;cursor: pointer;}
        .a-tip-text {
            float:left;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
通用上传按钮样式交互
<br/>
<a href="javascript:;" class="a-upload"><input type="file" name="myFiles" ><span>上传文件</span></a> <span class="a-tip-text">未上传任何文件</span>
<div class="tip-error">
    信用修复批量体检名单文件.xls <span class="bt-error-close"></span>
</div>
<script>

</script>
</body>
</html>